For example, we collect information you provide via any of our customer service channels including via phone, email, SMS and chat, and such information and your communications may be monitored, recorded, disclosed, reviewed, accessed and used by us and our third party vendors to improve the quality of goods and services we provide and the quality of services provided by our third party vendors.
