Before concluding the purchase contract, we carry out a fraud and credit check. This is done to enable us to offer you a choice of different payment methods and at the same time to protect ourselves against the default of payment of the invoice. As part of the credit check, we i.a. check all previously made orders in your customer account. It is also checked whether the delivery address differs from the billing address, whether the delivery address is new or if the order should be delivered to a pack station. For orders made in
